name: Nodeschool Stream
body:
### INTERNATIONAL NODE DAY is here on the 21st of May

No chapter near you? 

Do not fear! 
Join us in the NODESCHOOL stream for some live coding and workshopper assistance.
More info and links to the stream coming soon!

Wanna stay on top of it? Follow our repository on GitHub https://github.com/lulusam/nodeschoolstream

Help us spread the word and grow the Node tribe!
 
![Got Node? ](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lulusam/nodeschoolstream/gh-pages/Alone%20on%20NODE%20DAY%20(8).png)

For more info on the local chapters and events see http://nodeschool.io/international-day/
